bolt.web.coffee.dependency
Interface DependencyResolver<T extends NamedDependency>

All Known Implementing Classes:
DependencyManager
public interface DependencyResolver<T extends NamedDependency>

An implementation prototype for an object which accepts NamedDependency implementers and provides look-up methods for resolving the added references.

Author:
Matt Bolt
